normal until close then stay for an extra few hours to clean the store up and prep for the next day by stocking shelves and counting registers Member Services Representative Teleperformance USA Joplin MO April 2018 to November 2018 I worked at Teleperformance as a member services representative for a contracted insurance company I would answer calls from members verify their identity under very strict HIPAA guidelines then resolve whatever issue they called about however I needed to This often involved doing a large amount of research in our extensive policy documentation and sometimes reaching out to providers or medical groups to ensure the best possible care was provided to our members During my brief time at this position I received multiple awards from my coworkers for my ability and willingness to assist them with their calls while I was between calls or on hold myself When another representative was having trouble with a particularly difficult case they would come to me first before asking our technical support staff Local Inventory Associate WIS International Joplin MO September 2018 to October 2018 I worked briefly as a local inventory associate mostly working Dollar General locations but sometimes other small stores We would show up at 7am or earlier and inventory the entire store with as few as three people Unlike the traveling job for WIS we would rarely ever stay in hotels and mostly traveled back home every night I was regularly the top counter or second highest ranked in our speed accuracy ranking system I left this position due to changes in management Temp Express Employment Ponca City OK July 2018 to September 2018 I worked as a temporary laborer at a variety of jobs in Ponca City It was mostly working for Dorada the chicken processing plant but would have the occasional change in pace to a different job At Dorada I was responsible for the thirdshift complete breakdown and cleaning of all equipment in the facility We would shut power off to everything disassemble it and use power washers and very powerful cleaning agents to sterilize the entire facility Another big job was working a pumpkin patch I weeded the patch for a few weeks then as they ripened I harvested the pumpkins and hauled them to our stockpile for transportation All of my work with Express Employment ended only because I no longer reside in Ponca City OK Traveling Inventory Associate WIS International Joplin MO January 2018 to July 2018 I was a traveling inventory associate and would travel every week to stay in a hotel and work at mostly Walmarts in the surrounding area sometimes other bigbox stores I would arrive at the job site readytowork at 7am and with around 30 other counters we would work our way through the entire store inventory to verify the stores count is accurate I was regularly a top5 counter in our speedaccuracy rankings and would often finish out the day by helping the rest of the top counters finish 13 of the store while most of the crew finished counting clothing I was trained on all departments so I could work anywhere they needed me instead of just going with the flow While I never achieved the pay of a toprank counter the reason I no longer work with WIS I was actually ranked as such in the system on almost all of our jobs Network Administrator Econolodge Anderson MO January 2016 to November 2017 I worked phone system as well Before I began employment here the internet service was the biggest complaint received and after that went to a 95 the hotel moved up hundreds of ranks in the entire chain from over 850 to under 80 This was not a full time job and to compensate for that I would work parttime doing other things at the hotel starting with some daily housekeeping and ending with my being night auditor as well as network administrator I left this position due to a change in ownership of the hotel I worked at Cashier Walmart Neosho MO October 2016 to March 2017 I worked as a frontcheckout
